metadata.name: Just a Seed
metadata.description:
Everything has to start with a seed. This little Devil has all the potential in the world to conjure magic and beauty in the world. Capture it if you can, and it shall certainly spread good energy into the world. Only 100 in existence. 

All the funds go to the Forming Fest musicians that make it into the second round of Forming. Funds stream directly to the Forming JuiceBox treasury. https://juicebox.money/v2/p/66
